                <div class="tit_nav">
                    <span class="tit_l">您所在位置：</span><a href="/Home/Index">首页</a><b>></b><span>案例信息</span>
                </div>
                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/1534" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">MIS-0079</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">8687 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">CIO崛起vs.CIO边缘化：“天汽模”信息化之路的思考</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">CIO  Rise  VS.  CIO  Marginalization—— The  Reflection  of  TQM’s  Information  Path</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">朱克珊，张琳等</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">天津大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">天津汽车模具有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">机械、电机工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">信息管理部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">11 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">CIO；CIO边缘化；企业信息化；信息化战略；协同设计制造</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">CIO;CIO marginalized;enterprise information technology;information technology strategy;collaborative design and manufacturing</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">信息时代的来临，使企业的竞争环境发生了巨大变化。信息技术的飞速发展，加速了全球经济一体化市场的形成，对企业的创新能力和应变能力提出了更高要求，传统制造业企业更是迎来了前所未有的挑战。推动信息技术的应用，实施制造业信息化工程，已经成为制造业企业的必行之路。然而，自2008年以来的IT技术消失论以及CIO边缘化的讨论层出不穷，一定程度上引起了企业IT人员的恐慌和不安。本案例选用装备制造业中信息化程度较高的汽车模具行业作为研究对象，以天津汽车模具有限公司（简称：天汽模）信息化建设的实践路径为主线，围绕不同发展阶段，信息化建设的重点、成效、以及组织方式展开分析。通过深入企业调研、关键人物访谈等方式，揭示了这个2003年转制后，不足200人的小厂，一跃发展成为国内同行业中规模最大、客户覆盖面最广、市场占有率最高的龙头企业的故事。通过案例讨论，使学生可以感受企业信息化实践的全过程，培养理论联系实际、分析问题、解决问题的能力，在为管理信息系统教学实践提供素材的同时，也为企业实施信息化项目提供有效指导。 </td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">With the coming of the Information Age, the competitive environment for enterprises has changed dramatically. The rapid development of information technology accelerate the formation of global economic integration market and put forward higher requirements for enterprises’  innovation and resilience capacity. Traditional manufacturing enterprises are confronted with unprecedented challenge. It has become an inevitable choice for these manufacturing enterprises to promote the application of information technology and implement the Manufacturing Information Engineering. However, for remarks on the disappearance of IT technology and CIO Marginalization has proliferated frequently since 2008, it to some extend caused the panic and anxiety to IT staff.
Our case set our target research object as the automotive mold industry which has reached a higher degree of information technology in equipment manufacturing. With a deep research for the information construction path of Tianjin Motor Dies Co. Ltd. (referred to as: TQM), we discuss its different developing stages, information technology focus, effectiveness, and the organization. Through in-depth company research and key informant interviews etc., we reveal the fact that after the restructuring in 2003, the former company with less than 200 workers has developed into the leading enterprise with the biggest scale, the highest market share and the most extensive coverage of customers. With the discussion of the case, the students can experience the whole process of enterprise information practices and gain ability in analyzing and solving problems with the combination of theory and practice. In providing teaching material of the management of information systems, we give enterprises effective guidance to implementation of information technology projects in the meantime.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2013</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《管理信息系统》、《IT 项目管理》、《ERP》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">企业信息化的建设 信息系统实施</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2014-05</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
